      "content": "it just feels so much like my usual anxiety attacks though. the feeling in my chest is very similar and i've been under so much stress lately. do u think it's more likely just the anxiety hitting me again? i'd really rather not go to the doctors if i can avoid it, they always make such a big deal out of nothing.",
